{"id":15322,"date":"2024-07-01T10:23:09","date_gmt":"2024-07-01T03:23:09","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=15322"},"modified":"2024-07-01T10:23:12","modified_gmt":"2024-07-01T03:23:12","slug":"chenh-nhau-11-trieu-dong-chon-hyundai-grand-i10-hay-kia-morning","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/chenh-nhau-11-trieu-dong-chon-hyundai-grand-i10-hay-kia-morning\/","title":{"rendered":"Ch\u00eanh nhau 11 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng, ch\u1ecdn Hyundai Grand i10 hay Kia Morning"},"content":{"rendered":"<p class=\"the-article-summary\">Ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac xe c\u1ee1 A t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Ngo\u00e0i Hyundai Grand i10 v\u00e0 Kia Morning, nh\u00f3m n\u00e0y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Toyota Wigo.<\/p>\n<div class=\"the-article-body\">\n<div class=\"z-photoviewer-wrapper z-thumbnail\" align=\"center\">\n<div class=\"z-photo-backdrop\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"z-img-popup\">\n<div class=\"z-img-popup-overlay\">\n<div class=\"z-photo-caption\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"z-img-container\">\n<div class=\"z-img-container-inner\">\n<div class=\"z-img-sub-inner\">\n<div class=\"z-lazyimage-container\">\n<div class=\"z-img\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"unveil\" src=\"https:\/\/photo.znews.vn\/w1920\/Uploaded\/yqdlmdxwp\/2024_06_26\/i10_morning_2.jpg\" alt=\"\" \/><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<table class=\"picture thumbnail nocaption\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic YqB-inimage-wrapper\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"unveil\" title=\"null\" src=\"https:\/\/photo.znews.vn\/w960\/Uploaded\/yqdlmdxwp\/2024_06_26\/i10_morning_2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-title=\"null\" \/><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n<p>\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u1ea3 2 h\u00e3ng xe H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 Kia v\u00e0 Hyundai \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac xe c\u1ee1 A g\u1ea7m th\u1ea5p. Trong \u0111\u00f3, Hyundai Grand i10 v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n facelift v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd v\u1ec1 ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t v\u00e0 trang b\u1ecb an to\u00e0n, trong khi Kia Morning \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua giai \u0111o\u1ea1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/p>\n<p>\u1ede b\u1ea3n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p, Hyundai Grand i10 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 2 bi\u1ebfn th\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 6 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n, gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u1edf m\u1ee9c 360-455 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Kia Morning c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 6 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam, gi\u00e1 ni\u00eam y\u1ebft t\u1eeb 349 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ebfn 424 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng.<\/p>\n<h3>Kia Morning thua thi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3<\/h3>\n<p>Hyundai Grand i10 hatchback s\u1edf h\u1eefu k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00e0i x r\u1ed9ng x cao l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t 3.815 x 1.680 x 1.520 mm c\u00f9ng chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i c\u01a1 s\u1edf 2.450 mm. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Kia Morning c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 3.595 x 1.595 x 1.495 mm v\u00e0 chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i c\u01a1 s\u1edf 2.400 mm. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e2m xe k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc 15 inch tr\u00ean c\u00e1c phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n cao nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p>Nh\u00ecn chung, Kia Morning t\u1ecf ra thua k\u00e9m kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Hyundai Grand i10 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u00e1c th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Kia Morning c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn m\u1eabu xe n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng d\u00f2ng xe nh\u1ecf nh\u1ea5t th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00f4t\u00f4 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/p>\n<div class=\"z-photoviewer-wrapper \" align=\"center\">\n<div class=\"z-photo-backdrop\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"z-img-popup\">\n<div class=\"z-img-popup-overlay\">\n<div class=\"z-photo-caption\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"z-img-container\">\n<div class=\"z-img-container-inner\">\n<div class=\"z-img-sub-inner\">\n<div class=\"z-lazyimage-container\">\n<div class=\"z-img\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"unveil loaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo.znews.vn\/w1920\/Uploaded\/yzizh\/2020_11_30\/Kia_Morning_X_Line_2020_zing_1.jpg\" alt=\"Hyundai Grand i10 anh 2\" width=\"2737\" height=\"1825\" \/><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"z-img-popup\">\n<div class=\"z-img-popup-overlay\">\n<div class=\"z-photo-caption\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"z-img-container\">\n<div class=\"z-img-container-inner\">\n<div class=\"z-img-sub-inner\">\n<div class=\"z-lazyimage-container\">\n<div class=\"z-img\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"unveil loaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo.znews.vn\/w1920\/Uploaded\/yqdlmdxwp\/2024_06_26\/Hyundai_Grand_i10_90.png\" alt=\"Hyundai Grand i10 anh 1\" width=\"898\" height=\"599\" \/><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<table class=\"picture gallery\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\">\n<div class=\"photoset-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"unveil loaded\" title=\"Hyundai Grand i10 \u1ea3nh 1\" src=\"https:\/\/photo.znews.vn\/w1200\/Uploaded\/yqdlmdxwp\/2024_06_26\/Hyundai_Grand_i10_90.png\" alt=\"Hyundai Grand i10 anh 1\" width=\"898\" height=\"599\" data-title=\"Hyundai Grand i10 \u1ea3nh 1\" \/><\/div>\n<div class=\"photoset-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"unveil loaded\" title=\"Hyundai Grand i10 \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https:\/\/photo.znews.vn\/w1200\/Uploaded\/yzizh\/2020_11_30\/Kia_Morning_X_Line_2020_zing_1.jpg\" alt=\"Hyundai Grand i10 anh 2\" width=\"2737\" height=\"1825\" data-title=\"Hyundai Grand i10 \u1ea3nh 2\" \/><\/div>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pCaption caption default-caption\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n<p>Hyundai Grand i10 hatchback phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n 1.2 AT sau n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u1edf ph\u1ea7n ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t. M\u1eabu xe n\u00e0y s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u1edbi c\u00f9ng k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1edbn h\u01a1n gi\u00fap t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00ed l\u00e0m m\u00e1t v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i \u0111a hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1.<\/p>\n<p>C\u1ea3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u1ea3n sau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i d\u00e1ng v\u1ebb th\u1ec3 thao, trong khi c\u1ee5m \u0111\u00e8n LED ban ng\u00e0y nay s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh x\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00e1 thay v\u00ec boomerang nh\u01b0 tr\u00ean phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n c\u0169.<\/p>\n<p>Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Kia Morning phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n X-Line s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t m\u0169i h\u1ed5 \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a d\u00f2ng xe th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u Kia. Ph\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t n\u00e0y n\u1eb1m ngay gi\u1eefa v\u00e0 n\u1ed1i li\u1ec1n c\u00e1c c\u1ee5m \u0111\u00e8n chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Kia Morning.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u00e8n LED ch\u1ea1y ban ng\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u00e0o b\u00ean trong c\u1ee5m \u0111\u00e8n chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng ch\u00ednh tr\u00ean Kia Morning. C\u1ea3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n X-Line \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u01a1n b\u1ea1c, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u1ed1p nh\u1ef1a \u0111en n\u1ed1i li\u1ec1n ra ph\u1ea7n h\u1ed1c b\u00e1nh.<\/p>\n<div class=\"z-photoviewer-wrapper \" align=\"center\">\n<div class=\"z-photo-backdrop\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"z-img-popup\">\n<div class=\"z-img-popup-overlay\">\n<div class=\"z-photo-caption\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"z-img-container\">\n<div class=\"z-img-container-inner\">\n<div class=\"z-img-sub-inner\">\n<div class=\"z-lazyimage-container\">\n<div class=\"z-img\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"loaded unveil\" src=\"https:\/\/photo.znews.vn\/w1920\/Uploaded\/yzizh\/2020_11_30\/Kia_Morning_X_Line_2020_zing_7.jpg\" alt=\"Hyundai Grand i10 anh 4\" width=\"3891\" height=\"2595\" \/><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"z-img-popup\">\n<div class=\"z-img-popup-overlay\">\n<div class=\"z-photo-caption\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"z-img-container\">\n<div class=\"z-img-container-inner\">\n<div class=\"z-img-sub-inner\">\n<div class=\"z-lazyimage-container\">\n<div class=\"z-img\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"loaded unveil\" src=\"https:\/\/photo.znews.vn\/w1920\/Uploaded\/yqdlmdxwp\/2024_06_14\/New_Grand_i10_Hatchback_3.jpg\" alt=\"Hyundai Grand i10 anh 3\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1366\" \/><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<table class=\"picture gallery\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\">\n<div class=\"photoset-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"loaded unveil\" title=\"Hyundai Grand i10 \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https:\/\/photo.znews.vn\/w1200\/Uploaded\/yqdlmdxwp\/2024_06_14\/New_Grand_i10_Hatchback_3.jpg\" alt=\"Hyundai Grand i10 anh 3\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1366\" \/><\/div>\n<div class=\"photoset-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"loaded unveil\" title=\"Hyundai Grand i10 \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https:\/\/photo.znews.vn\/w1200\/Uploaded\/yzizh\/2020_11_30\/Kia_Morning_X_Line_2020_zing_7.jpg\" alt=\"Hyundai Grand i10 anh 4\" width=\"3891\" height=\"2595\" data-title=\"Hyundai Grand i10 \u1ea3nh 4\" \/><\/div>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pCaption caption default-caption\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n<p>C\u1ea3 2 m\u1eabu xe \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb b\u00f3ng halogen projector cho c\u1ee5m \u0111\u00e8n chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng ch\u00ednh, c\u00f3 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1eadt\/t\u1eaft. Kia Morning \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam \u0111\u00e8n s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ea3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, trong khi chi ti\u1ebft n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean Hyundai Grand i10.<\/p>\n<h3>N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t &#8211; k\u1ebb t\u00e1m l\u1ea1ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1eeda c\u00e2n<\/h3>\n<p>Do s\u1edf h\u1eefu tr\u1ee5c c\u01a1 s\u1edf t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i ng\u1eafn, kh\u00f4ng gian khoang l\u00e1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kia Morning tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Hyundai Grand i10. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, nh\u1eefng trang b\u1ecb b\u00ean trong khoang n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Kia Morning v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac.<\/p>\n<p>Ph\u00eda sau v\u00f4 l\u0103ng b\u1ecdc da, c\u1ea3 Hyundai Grand i10 l\u1eabn Kia Morning \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u0111a th\u00f4ng tin, hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n xe. T\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung t\u00e2m t\u00e1p-l\u00f4, Hyundai Grand i10 v\u00e0 Kia Morning c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc 8 inch, c\u00f3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i Apple CarPlay v\u00e0 Android Auto.<\/p>\n<div class=\"z-photoviewer-wrapper \" align=\"center\">\n<div class=\"z-photo-backdrop\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"z-img-popup\">\n<div class=\"z-img-popup-overlay\">\n<div class=\"z-photo-caption\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"z-img-container\">\n<div class=\"z-img-container-inner\">\n<div class=\"z-img-sub-inner\">\n<div class=\"z-lazyimage-container\">\n<div class=\"z-img\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"loaded unveil\" src=\"https:\/\/photo.znews.vn\/w1920\/Uploaded\/yzizh\/2020_11_30\/Kia_Morning_X_Line_2020_zing_13.jpg\" alt=\"Hyundai Grand i10 anh 6\" width=\"3758\" height=\"2505\" \/><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"z-img-popup\">\n<div class=\"z-img-popup-overlay\">\n<div class=\"z-photo-caption\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"z-img-container\">\n<div class=\"z-img-container-inner\">\n<div class=\"z-img-sub-inner\">\n<div class=\"z-lazyimage-container\">\n<div class=\"z-img\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"loaded unveil\" src=\"https:\/\/photo.znews.vn\/w1920\/Uploaded\/yqdlmdxwp\/2024_06_26\/New_Grand_i10_92.jpg\" alt=\"Hyundai Grand i10 anh 5\" width=\"2028\" height=\"1352\" \/><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<table class=\"picture gallery\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\">\n<div class=\"photoset-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"loaded unveil\" title=\"Hyundai Grand i10 \u1ea3nh 5\" src=\"https:\/\/photo.znews.vn\/w1200\/Uploaded\/yqdlmdxwp\/2024_06_26\/New_Grand_i10_92.jpg\" alt=\"Hyundai Grand i10 anh 5\" width=\"2028\" height=\"1352\" \/><\/div>\n<div class=\"photoset-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"loaded unveil\" title=\"Hyundai Grand i10 \u1ea3nh 6\" src=\"https:\/\/photo.znews.vn\/w1200\/Uploaded\/yzizh\/2020_11_30\/Kia_Morning_X_Line_2020_zing_13.jpg\" alt=\"Hyundai Grand i10 anh 6\" width=\"3758\" height=\"2505\" \/><\/div>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pCaption caption default-caption\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Hyundai Grand i10 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat so v\u1edbi trang b\u1ecb tr\u00ean Kia Morning do c\u00f3 t\u00edch h\u1ee3p h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb d\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Hyundai nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/p>\n<p>Hyundai Grand i10 c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean duy nh\u1ea5t trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac xe c\u1ee1 A g\u1ea7m th\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb Cruise Control c\u00f9ng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng s\u1ea5y g\u01b0\u01a1ng chi\u1ebfu h\u1eadu. Hyundai Grand i10 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda gi\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a cho h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf sau, \u0111\u00e8n n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 4 t\u00fai kh\u00ed, nh\u1eefng trang b\u1ecb hi\u1ebfm th\u1ea5y trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac \u00f4t\u00f4 c\u1ee1 nh\u1ecf.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, Kia Morning l\u1ea1i &#8220;ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m&#8221; nh\u1edd h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u00e0 h\u00e3ng xe H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c trang b\u1ecb cho m\u1eabu xe c\u1ee1 A. Tr\u00ean Hyundai Grand i10, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a v\u1eabn l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9nh c\u01a1, c\u00f2n \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a tr\u00ean Toyota Wigo c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/p>\n<p>Kia Morning c\u0169ng c\u00f3 b\u1ec7 t\u00ec tay cho gh\u1ebf l\u00e1i l\u00e0 trang b\u1ecb ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ebf s\u1ea1c kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean c\u00e1c phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n X-Line v\u00e0 GT-Line. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ed5ng s\u1ea1c Type-C c\u0169ng l\u00e0 trang b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd v\u1eeba xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean Hyundai Grand i10 b\u1ea3n facelift.<\/p>\n<h3>T\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhau v\u1ec1 an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh<\/h3>\n<p>B\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi n\u1eafp ca-p\u00f4, Hyundai Grand i10 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 Kappa dung t\u00edch 1.2L, s\u1ea3n sinh c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t t\u1ed1i \u0111a 83 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c c\u00f9ng m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1i 114 Nm. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Kia Morning s\u1edf h\u1eefu kh\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 dung t\u00edch 1.25L, cho ra c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t t\u1ed1i \u0111a t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n, \u1edf m\u1ee9c 122 Nm.<\/p>\n<div class=\"z-photoviewer-wrapper \" align=\"center\">\n<div class=\"z-photo-backdrop\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"z-img-popup\">\n<div class=\"z-img-popup-overlay\">\n<div class=\"z-photo-caption\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"z-img-container\">\n<div class=\"z-img-container-inner\">\n<div class=\"z-img-sub-inner\">\n<div class=\"z-lazyimage-container\">\n<div class=\"z-img\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"loaded unveil\" src=\"https:\/\/photo.znews.vn\/w1920\/Uploaded\/yqdlmdxwp\/2022_07_11\/Kia_Morning_X_Line_2020.jpg\" alt=\"Hyundai Grand i10 anh 8\" width=\"2849\" height=\"1899\" \/><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"z-img-popup\">\n<div class=\"z-img-popup-overlay\">\n<div class=\"z-photo-caption\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"z-img-container\">\n<div class=\"z-img-container-inner\">\n<div class=\"z-img-sub-inner\">\n<div class=\"z-lazyimage-container\">\n<div class=\"z-img\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"loaded unveil\" src=\"https:\/\/photo.znews.vn\/w1920\/Uploaded\/yqdlmdxwp\/2024_06_14\/New_Grand_i10_hatchback_9.jpg\" alt=\"Hyundai Grand i10 anh 7\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" \/><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<table class=\"picture gallery\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\">\n<div class=\"photoset-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"loaded unveil\" title=\"Hyundai Grand i10 \u1ea3nh 7\" src=\"https:\/\/photo.znews.vn\/w1200\/Uploaded\/yqdlmdxwp\/2024_06_14\/New_Grand_i10_hatchback_9.jpg\" alt=\"Hyundai Grand i10 anh 7\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" \/><\/div>\n<div class=\"photoset-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"loaded unveil\" title=\"Hyundai Grand i10 \u1ea3nh 8\" src=\"https:\/\/photo.znews.vn\/w1200\/Uploaded\/yqdlmdxwp\/2022_07_11\/Kia_Morning_X_Line_2020.jpg\" alt=\"Hyundai Grand i10 anh 8\" width=\"2849\" height=\"1899\" \/><\/div>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pCaption caption default-caption\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n<p>C\u1ea3 Hyundai Grand i10 hatchback b\u1ea3n 1.2 AT l\u1eabn Kia Morning phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n X-Line \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng 4 c\u1ea5p k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp ph\u00eda tr\u00ean, &#8220;d\u00e0n ch\u00e2n&#8221; c\u1ee7a hai xe \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 m\u00e2m k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc 15 inch, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb phanh \u0111\u0129a tr\u00ean tr\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 phanh tang tr\u1ed1ng \u1edf tr\u1ee5c sau.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1ec1 trang b\u1ecb an to\u00e0n, Hyundai Grand i10 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n nh\u1edd h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng Cruise Control, c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn \u00e1p su\u1ea5t l\u1ed1p c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi 4 t\u00fai kh\u00ed. C\u1ea3 2 xe \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng an to\u00e0n ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n nh\u01b0 ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3 c\u1ee9ng phanh, c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 kh\u1edfi h\u00e0nh ngang d\u1ed1c, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 xe ph\u00eda sau v\u00e0 camera l\u00f9i.<\/p>\n<h3>Gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch<\/h3>\n<p>\u1edeb\u1ea3n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p, Hyundai Grand i10 hatchback b\u1ea3n 1.2 AT v\u1eabn c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 ni\u00eam y\u1ebft 435 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Kia Morning X-Line hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 ni\u00eam y\u1ebft 424 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng.<\/p>\n<p>Kho\u1ea3ng ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch 11 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng qua c\u00e1c trang b\u1ecb kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean Hyundai Grand i10 nh\u01b0 Cruise Control, 4 t\u00fai kh\u00ed hay s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Kia Morning l\u1ea1i n\u1ed5i tr\u1ed9i nh\u1edd s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng hay ngo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 thao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/p>\n<p>Sau 5 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m, Hyundai Grand i10 \u0111ang t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi l\u00e0 m\u1eabu xe c\u1ee1 A b\u00e1n ch\u1ea1y nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac v\u1edbi doanh s\u1ed1 1.889 xe. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Kia Morning t\u1ecf ra t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt khi doanh s\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u1eddng k\u1ef3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua m\u1ed1c 75 xe, khi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 t\u00edch l\u0169y sau 5 th\u00e1ng \u0111ang t\u1ea1m d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf 320 xe.<\/p>\n<div id=\"chart-229\" class=\"chart-wrapper\" data-highcharts-chart=\"0\">\n<div id=\"highcharts-2b9zi80-0\" class=\"highcharts-container \" dir=\"ltr\">Hyundai Grand i10 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 xe c\u1ee1 A b\u00e1n ch\u1ea1y nh\u1ea5tC\u01a1 c\u1ea5u doanh s\u1ed1 ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac xe c\u1ee1 A t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau 5 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m (S\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u: VAMA, TC Motor)Hyundai Grand i10Hyundai Grand i10Toyota WigoToyota WigoKia MorningKia Morning<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>Sau khi Toyota Wigo quay l\u1ea1i h\u1ed3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1edbi di\u1ec7n m\u1ea1o m\u1edbi c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p, c\u00f2n Hyundai Grand i10 c\u0169ng v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u b\u1ea3n c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Kia Morning th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 ti\u1ebfp theo nh\u1eb1m c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ednh c\u1ea1nh tranh.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac xe c\u1ee1 A t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Ngo\u00e0i Hyundai Grand i10 v\u00e0 Kia Morning, nh\u00f3m n\u00e0y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Toyota Wigo. &nbsp; \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u1ea3 2 h\u00e3ng xe H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 Kia v\u00e0 [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":15323,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"yst_prominent_words":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15322"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=15322"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15322\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":15325,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-